description: DECISION AND ORDER: It is hereby ORDERED that the #  36     MOTION to Dismiss for Failure to State a Claim   filed by Saratoga Center for Care LLC, Danielle Zastawny is DENIED without prejudice to re-filing. Defendant may file a renewed motion  to dismiss within fourteen days of the date of this order. If Defendant files such a motion, the Court will set a briefing schedule. If Defendant fails to file such a motion, Defendant shall file an answer to the Complaint within 21 days of the date  of this order. Plaintiff's #  40  letter motion seeking an update on the status of Defendant's motion is hereby DENIED as moot. The above decision and order provides that update.  Signed by Senior Judge Thomas J. McAvoy on 4/25/2022. {Copy served upon pro se Plaintiff via regular mail}(pjh, )
